node.text: (link in bio) We talk about her passion for being in tune with nature. She shares how she encourages open communication with her children, appreciating nature as it is while learning to appreciate our own value, and the healing benefits of incorporating meditation in your daily routine.

Inspired by a true story shared by Thomas McFall - names and events in the story have been modified in this video.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jay Shetty on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Fee like something's missing? Your spirit is telling you to slow down and enjoy this moment. GENIUS JAY SHETTY'.

node.text:
Listen to your spirit 🙏 Give @jayshettygenius a follow and comment a YES below if you agree.⁠⁠
⁠⁠
@jayshettygenius is what happens when weekly coaching, dedicated meditation, and vibrant community all come together. This is the space where I share my private workshops and guided meditations for mind, body, and soul. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
It's all about coaching 🙌 consistency 💫 and community ❤️ ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
And I'd love for you to join me in next Sunday's workshop!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Link in bio to join Genius today 🔗 jayshettygenius.com

node.text: (link in bio) We talk about her passion for being in tune with nature. She shares how she encourages open communication with her children, appreciating nature as it is while learning to appreciate our own value, and the healing benefits of incorporating meditation in your daily routine.

node.text:
@radhidevlukia can even make 💩 fun and entertaining! Happy Sunday Everyone! 

5 THINGS TO TRY TO HELP YOU 💩

1. SPICE UP YOUR LIFE - cumin, coriander and fennel aid digestion and relax stomach muscles. Saute and add them into your curries or roast the seeds and grind all 3 spices into powder and sprinkle onto anything! 

2. KEEP IT MOVING🏃🏾‍♀️
Aerobic exercise increases blood flow to digestive organs and increases strength h of intestinal muscles 

3. CHEW PROPERLY - the more you chew the easier it is to digest the easier it is to 💩

4. STOMACH MASSAGE
- 5-10 mins relaxes muscles and moves it along! 

 5 TRIPHALA POWDER 
- a natural laxitive. Take 1/2 tsp in 1/2 cup warm water before bed. 

Happy 💩ing

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jay Shetty on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'We need to stop glamorizing overworking. Please. The absence of sleep, good diet, exercise, relaxation, and time with friends and family isn't something to be applauded. Too many people wear their burnout as a badge of honor and it needs to change @katyleeson/Twitter'.

node.text: Drop a ❤️ below if you’re making time to recover this weekend👇 If you truly want to achieve your goals. If you really want to make an impact. Rest & recovery are huge parts of your toolkit. Observe the life of any athlete and you will see how this isn’t a reaction to burnout, or fatigue it’s part of their conditioning and training. Incorporate this into your life and watch how it changes!
